                                                        <tr style="border-collapse:collapse">
                                                            <td align="left" style="padding:0;Margin:0;padding-bottom:25px"><h2 style="Margin:0;font-family:tahoma, verdana, segoe, sans-serif;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;letter-spacing:0;font-size:24px;font-style:normal;font-weight:bold;line-height:28.8px;color:#4A4A4A"><strong>Gentili Fornitori,</strong></h2></td>
                                                        </tr>
                                                        <tr style="border-collapse:collapse">
                                                            <td align="left" class="c" style="padding:0;Margin:0"><p style="Margin:0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:helvetica, 'helvetica neue', arial, verdana, sans-serif;line-height:22.5px;letter-spacing:0;color:#4A4A4A;font-size:15px">Desideriamo informarvi che è in fase di implementazione un nuovo portale per migliorare la gestione dello scambio di documentazione tra Metallurgica Bresciana e i suoi fornitori.</p><p style="Margin:0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:helvetica, 'helvetica neue', arial, verdana, sans-serif;line-height:22.5px;letter-spacing:0;color:#4A4A4A;font-size:15px"><br></p><p style="Margin:0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:helvetica, 'helvetica neue', arial, verdana, sans-serif;line-height:22.5px;letter-spacing:0;color:#4A4A4A;font-size:15px">Questo portale vi permetterà di rispondere in autonomia ai questionari di qualifica, caricare certificati, ricevere avvisi e comunicazioni sulle non conformità.</p><p style="Margin:0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:helvetica, 'helvetica neue', arial, verdana, sans-serif;line-height:22.5px;letter-spacing:0;color:#4A4A4A;font-size:15px"><br></p><p style="Margin:0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:helvetica, 'helvetica neue', arial, verdana, sans-serif;line-height:22.5px;letter-spacing:0;color:#4A4A4A;font-size:15px">Come primo passo, vi chiediamo cortesemente di fornirci i nominativi (nome e cognome) e i relativi indirizzi email dei vostri referenti per le seguenti aree:</p><p style="Margin:0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:helvetica, 'helvetica neue', arial, verdana, sans-serif;line-height:22.5px;letter-spacing:0;color:#4A4A4A;font-size:15px"><br></p><p class="b" style="Margin:0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:helvetica, 'helvetica neue', arial, verdana, sans-serif;line-height:19.5px;letter-spacing:0;color:#4A4A4A;font-size:13px"><strong>* Qualità:</strong></p><p class="b" style="Margin:0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:helvetica, 'helvetica neue', arial, verdana, sans-serif;line-height:19.5px;letter-spacing:0;color:#4A4A4A;font-size:13px"><strong>* Ambiente:</strong></p><p class="b" style="Margin:0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:helvetica, 'helvetica neue', arial, verdana, sans-serif;line-height:19.5px;letter-spacing:0;color:#4A4A4A;font-size:13px"><strong>* Sicurezza:</strong></p><p class="b" style="Margin:0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:helvetica, 'helvetica neue', arial, verdana, sans-serif;line-height:19.5px;letter-spacing:0;color:#4A4A4A;font-size:13px"><strong>* SA8000:</strong></p><p class="b" style="Margin:0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:helvetica, 'helvetica neue', arial, verdana, sans-serif;line-height:19.5px;letter-spacing:0;color:#4A4A4A;font-size:13px"><strong><br></strong></p><p class="b" style="Margin:0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:helvetica, 'helvetica neue', arial, verdana, sans-serif;line-height:19.5px;letter-spacing:0;color:#4A4A4A;font-size:13px"><strong> </strong>Siete pregati quindi&nbsp;di fornirci&nbsp;le informazioni richieste sopra entro 5 gg dalla ricezione della presente mail.</p><p class="b" style="Margin:0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:helvetica, 'helvetica neue', arial, verdana, sans-serif;line-height:19.5px;letter-spacing:0;color:#4A4A4A;font-size:13px"><br></p><p class="b" style="Margin:0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:helvetica, 'helvetica neue', arial, verdana, sans-serif;line-height:19.5px;letter-spacing:0;color:#4A4A4A;font-size:13px">Vi ringraziamo per la collaborazione,</p><p class="b" style="Margin:0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:helvetica, 'helvetica neue', arial, verdana, sans-serif;line-height:19.5px;letter-spacing:0;color:#4A4A4A;font-size:13px"><br></p><p class="b" style="Margin:0;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;font-family:helvetica, 'helvetica neue', arial, verdana, sans-serif;line-height:19.5px;letter-spacing:0;color:#4A4A4A;font-size:13px">Cordiali saluti. <strong> </strong></p></td>
                                                        </tr>
